            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/></supplied> Cominio <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/></supplied> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Claud</abbr><ex>ia</ex></expan> Bono <lb n="3"/>Agricolae L<supplied reason="lost">a</supplied>elio <lb n="4"/>Apro <expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ecto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr><supplied reason="lost">c</supplied>ohort</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>tert</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Bracaraugustano</abbr><ex>rum</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>tribun</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost">I</supplied> <expan><abbr>adiut</abbr><ex>ricis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>procur</abbr><ex>atori</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>Augustorum ad annonam <lb n="8"/>provinciae Narbonensis <lb n="9"/>et Liguriae <expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ecto</ex></expan> a<supplied reason="lost">lae</supplied> miliariae <lb n="10"/>in Mauretania Caesariensi <lb n="11"/><expan><abbr>navic</abbr><ex>ulariorum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>marin</abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Arel</abbr><ex>atensium</ex></expan> <lb n="12"/><expan><abbr>corp</abbr><ex>ora</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>quinq</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>patron</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <lb n="13"/>optimo et innocentis<lb break="no" n="14"/>simo
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): Z.2/3: AE, Christol: [- f(ilio) C]laud(ia) Bo[v]io / Agricol[ae Aur]elio. CIL: BO[--]I[--] Agricola[e Aur]elio; ILS: Agricola[e Aur]elio. (C): Datierung Ende 2.Jh./Anfang 3.Jh. Y: Die Prokuratur fällt in die Regierungszeit von M. Aurel u. Verus. Material: grauer Kalkstein.</p>
